      "rationale": "A single mesh of 4.2 million elements was used for all production runs. A coarse mesh comparison was performed at one operating point only, yielding a qualitative assessment of mesh adequacy. No formal GCI computation was performed and the Richardson extrapolation procedure was not applied. The team judged the mesh sufficiently fine based on y+ values near the impeller blades, but this does not constitute a systematic grid convergence study as required at Gradation 3."
    },
