      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental conditions replicated: inlet flow 2.5 L/min and 5.0 L/min, rotational speeds 2000–3500 RPM, fluid temperature 37°C, blood analog viscosity matched. Boundary condition uncertainty documented."
