    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 V&V 40 factors. Seven factors were formally assessed and all were judged to meet or exceed required levels. Six factors were not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The team declares High assurance based on the strong performance of assessed factors and the overall robustness of the validation evidence package. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
